Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.32,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.40,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This is Kawajiri Kosaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:18.33,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I understand this is incredibly selfish of me, \Nbut I'm going to be fifteen minutes late to the office today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:24.08,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes. My son is misbehaving, and I have to discipline him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:30.09,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir. I completely understand that \Nanyone else would find my excuse trivial at best. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.51,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.59,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes, the moment I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:39.10,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll head directly to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.14,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.10,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes. Please excuse me, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:51.40,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn that spineless Kawajiri Kosaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:55.82,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Was climbing the corporate ladder that important to him? \NActing like that is so stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:08.42,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Josuke escaped inside this house since he knew \Nforcing us to fight in close quarters would give him the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I must agree, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:17.59,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's in my best interest to avoid \Na close-quarters fight with Crazy Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:25.14,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If I can figure out Josuke's exact location, \NI can shoot him from here with an air bullet. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.69,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.94,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Just what do you think you're doing on this property?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:38.57,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, is that how it is? \NTrying to tell me you're {\i1}not{\i0} on this property?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.24,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't get technical with me, Mr. Nice Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.83,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Is this your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.29,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,How long have you been watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:48.42,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one asking questions here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.13,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'll have you know I live next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:55.26,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I was {\i1}hoping{\i0} I'd get to sleep past noon today,\N but I got woken up by a loud noise outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.97,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You're a suspicious guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:01.05,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The cute girl who lives here, Rio,\N is always telling me about how her panties get stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.93,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,And since nobody is normally around here at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.73,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:06.68,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,To have so much free time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.98,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, you running away from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:14.19,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Shit! He's got some nerve, going after Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.94,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.79,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,So he {\i1}is{\i0} a panty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.66,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,These panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.80,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-These are Rio's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.52,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,...p-p-pan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:52.56,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yippee! I'm so lucky!
Comment: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,OPENING
Comment: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:17.94,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:23.65,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,513)\pos(135,890)\fs60}Episode 38: {\fs80} Crazy Diamond is Unbreakable Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.58,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's no use! The phone's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.05,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:49.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat the hell out of Kira Yoshikage \Nwith Crazy Diamond until he can't move a muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:53.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,In a few minutes, this will all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.73,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Stay back against the wall. \NOtherwise, Kira will see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But where exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.83,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...is he gonna come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.52,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:38.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Wh{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.32,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.48,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.40,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's an air bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.53,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,There's one headed right for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.12,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's the same size as the one from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.16,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,B-But that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.66,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,There's no way he can know where you are from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.92,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,How does he know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.46,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I know how far away you are, Higashikata Josuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I know right where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Three meters until impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.10,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.90,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,The ball of air is visible now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.19,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.69,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Now he can dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:29.16,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,No matter how many are sent after him,\N he'll be able to dodge... them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.62,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.41,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's going after Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Kira Yoshikage somehow knows exactly where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Where is he? How can he see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.68,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,There weren't any windows in that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.51,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,All of the curtains are drawn, too! {wat? why are ther curtains with no windows?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.89,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,There's no way he can see you from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.27,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's automatic! It must be automatically chasing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:08.94,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Sheer Heart Attack is the only ability of Killer Queen's that automatically goes after heat sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.70,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This thing is completely ignoring the lit cigarette!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:17.95,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no way the bullet could be automatically homing in on me after going through a solid wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:24.34,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...and Kira definitely wants to trigger\N the final detonation that finishes me off himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:28.59,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't know how, but he knows exactly where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.84,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's getting faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.34,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Find Kira for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.51,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Figure out how he's watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.89,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-I see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.68,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He's right outside the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:44.15,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Two meters until impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.40,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,He's outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:50.99,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have no idea how he's tracking you from there, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.49,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run away! {it was "Hurry up" through all of 37}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You asshole!\N I have no idea how you're watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.24,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,One more meter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:03.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but I have no intention of trying to hide from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.33,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Crazy Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.25,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Good, it's going to hit Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.01,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Detonate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes! It was a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.77,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.56,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My, my, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.48,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Good thing I was on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:30.82,Main,Kra,0,0,0,,I'm impressed that you had the willpower\N to deal one final, desperate blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:35.53,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This is why I refuse to get\N anywhere near you, Higashikata Josuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.83,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.95,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.79,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Hmph. It was a direct hit, \Nbut it didn't blow him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:49.13,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Detonating by hand is slightly \Nless accurate than doing it automatically...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.88,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...but he can't undo the damage he's received. {should this be "heal" or some reference to his ability?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.30,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My next shot will finish him for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.51,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,W-We...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.97,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,We have to get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Y-You're pulling me in the wrong direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:08.40,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Go the other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.57,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Not that way... Go the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill him! {should this be "beat" or something? Josuke seemed to be ready to beat him up til he cant move, not kill}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I need you to drag me towards Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.62,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,My Crazy Diamond...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.95,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...can't heal my own wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:28.96,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But once my blood has left my body, \N it becomes like any other object.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.63,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It stops being part of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can gather it up and stick it onto other objects!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's why I put some of it inside a shard of glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:44.77,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Now that the rain stopped, \Nthe blood stain he got on his jacket earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.89,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...should have dried up by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.73,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}my{\i0} automatic homing attack!
Comment: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:09.50,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The shard of glass I just guarded myself from...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.00,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,He must have used the blood stain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.51,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The stain must have led the glass shard right to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.51,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Y-You hit him dead on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.47,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's deep inside Kira's back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:36.53,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Higashikata Josuke and his damned Crazy Diamond...\N I can't predict the actions of him {\i1}or{\i0} his Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:40.53,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Still, Josuke has sustained much more damage than I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Just one more shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:46.95,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,One more shot and I, Kira Yoshikage, will be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.63,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:57.01,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He sent one big enough to see from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,No doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's his final shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.64,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This will be mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:10.85,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-I don't think the same attack will work on Kira twice! \NHe'll guard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:15.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Well... I had to try just to know for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:21.57,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Hayato. Sorry to ask you this,\N but there's a lighter in my pocket that I used earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.57,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Can you grab it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:28.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll be able to grab it myself with this piece of wood sticking out of my stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.71,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,The smoke is useless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.42,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You can see this air bullet without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:36.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm not using the lighter to see the air bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I need it to look at something else. Grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.31,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Let's figure out how he can see me once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't move, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.15,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,J-Josuke? Wh-What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.52,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hold still, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,He may not be watching us after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.95,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I think he's listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.74,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Kira was holding a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.08,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Is that just a coincidence? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But who was he talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.33,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Was it his boss from the office? \NNo, not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:18.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,There's only one person Kira would be\N calling at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:32.56,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I almost completely forgot about you,\N old man in the photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:37.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You've been trying to protect\N Kira Yoshikage this entire time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:41.69,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have no idea when he got inside my pocket, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:45.16,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,This was our answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:50.20,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-The air bullet passed through the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.00,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.21,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,It hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:01.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Josuke... is running away three meters ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.47,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.97,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It passed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:14.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Now, he's moving diagonally right and up three meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:19.82,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,He doesn't realize that it's just \NJosuke talking to him in a raspy voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:26.16,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Now, he's running away, one meter to the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:30.53,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,What?! How could you do this to me, you thug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.66,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Right there! Detonate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.79,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.89,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I did it! Josuke was completely blown away, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.89,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah, he went out in a blaze of glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.81,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,My directions sent him straight to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:14:01.07,Narrator,Josuke,0,0,0,,Then again, he was just a ghost, \Nso I guess you could say he crossed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.65,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Josuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.78,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:16.25,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Th-This must be some kind of... mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.37,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Something this horrific...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:26.26,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...should never have happened... during my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:32.01,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,All I asked for was to live a life of peace, like a plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:40.27,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,However, at times like these...  \Nsomething I shouldn't forget... during such bad situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.31,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,...such {\i1}horrible{\i0} situations like this... {"bad situations and horrible situations"...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.03,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,...is that there's always a chance for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.03,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,My past has taught me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:54.24,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,As long as I think things through rationally,\N despite being backed into a corner, my chance to win will surely come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:58.79,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I just need to do the same as I, \NKira Yoshikage, have always done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:05.09,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,There isn't any kind of trouble I'm incapable of overcoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.76,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,None!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:19.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're finally within my range...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.66,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He's close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:35.03,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He finally got close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.58,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Since it's a close-quarters fight, it'll be over in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:45.79,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Josuke's ability is stronger, \Nb-but if Kira touches him, he'll be turned into a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:51.68,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,N-Not to mention,\NJosuke still has wounds on his legs and torso from that blast...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:56.35,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Josuke, it's a miracle you can even stand right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.85,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Higashikata Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:05.61,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Bring out... your Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.87,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:24.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.35,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,H-He's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.81,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.23,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I, Kira Yoshikage, am going to be utterly defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:50.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:55.61,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,N-No way... There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:59.74,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,We were so close! \NJosuke is so much stronger than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:04.50,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Is fate really on the side of that serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:10.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,M-My fists didn't connect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,These are air bubbles! \NThey cushioned the blows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:18.18,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,B-But I wasn't trying to guard myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.89,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I had no time to consider that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.06,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Stray Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:30.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That's it! Stray Cat thought it was being attacked, \Nso it instinctively blocked his attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.53,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,My chance! I've found my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.70,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,A chance finally presented itself at this horrible time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.32,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.41,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Change that air bullet into a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.20,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.42,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I changed it into a contact bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.13,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Anyone who touches it will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:55.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Josuke, with all of the damage you've sustained, \Nyou won't have the strength to dodge this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.05,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.22,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's a contact bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:04.93,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Josuke! It doesn't matter if you use glass or even wood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.98,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hit it with something and take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:14.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I win! Something like this always happens\N after life deals me a bad hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.82,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Luck truly {\i1}is{\i0} on the side of Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.50,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:29.96,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-The air bullet is going off course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.13,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.51,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.01,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.51,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\i1}...O-Okuyasu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:45.18,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Y'know, I always wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:51.02,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Where's all the stuff that gets erased by The Hand go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:56.36,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I ain't too bright, an' it gives me \Nheadaches thinkin' about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.15,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.61,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:02.57,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-I can't believe it! I-It's Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.54,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,But his heart stopped, and he wasn't breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:10.37,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I was just havin' a funny dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:18.26,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I was walkin' in the dark or somethin', an' I saw a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.93,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,My dead big bro was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.18,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,My big bro, Keicho.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:33.44,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He says to me "Where're you goin', Okuyasu?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:37.44,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,An' I said "I'm just followin' you, big bro."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.57,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Only made sense since\N I could always count on my big bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:45.45,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He ain't never made a bad choice, \Nso I wasn't worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:50.96,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,But then he says to me: \N"Ya gotta choose where you're goin' for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.75,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Okuyasu, you're the one who's gotta\N decide where you're gonna go."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.72,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I thought about it real hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:05.47,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,...an' I told him I was goin' \Nback t'Morioh, then I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.85,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Made me feel real sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:17.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...y-you're really pushing it, dreaming at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:24.61,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ya don't gotta be like that! \NYou're actually lookin' pretty good for all the beatin' you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.08,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:30.83,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You should have woken up sooner \Nif you weren't really dead, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:37.96,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I-Impossible...\NFate was supposed to be on the side of I, Kira Yoshikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.09,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.09,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Stray Cat! Shoot another bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.43,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.44,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Whoa! Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:21:00.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! Now Kira won't be able to\N use his air bullet bombs anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Th-Th-There's never...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:15.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,There's never been any trouble that I, Kira Yoshikage,\N couldn't overcome with enough effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.42,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Look, Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.50,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,The loud noise we heard must have come from that house!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:23.17,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,What do you think happened? A gas explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:27.68,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,L-Look over there! That man is injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.28,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Josuke and Okuyasu are there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.24,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,That child is Kawajiri Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.70,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,And the man is Kawajiri Kosaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.29,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Looks like everything is finally coming together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.54,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Any fate that would side with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:03.59,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Any chance that would come your way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:09.26,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,They're nothing compared to \Nthe spirit of justice that's here right now! {These last three lines are in 39 and current as of blu-ray check}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:14.52,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's definitely here! There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:16.98,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Compared to that spirit, you're nothing!
